name: Pune Java User Group
body:
### Welcome to Pune Java User Group

If you are interested in anything that runs on the JVM, join our [Meetup](http://www.meetup.com/PuneJUG) group and show up at our next meet up. 

Following are the links where you can find more about us: 

[Meetup](http://www.meetup.com/PuneJUG) |
[Twitter](http://twitter.com/JavaPune) | 
[Github](https://github.com/PuneJUG) |
[Google Groups](http://groups.google.com/group/javapune) |
[LinkedIn](http://www.linkedin.com/groups/Pune-Java-User-Group-3206756) |
[Facebook](http://www.facebook.com/JavaPune)
